channel.title: What port # do you forward? Fast reply would be nice
channel.description:
Im not asking how to port forward. I know how. But what port # are you forwarding? 43594, or something else? Ive tried 53494, and I still cant get in. BTW, I have testscape, and the private server tut I saw gave me the code to put in my compile.bat for nixscape. Will the nixscape thing work for testscape? Or do I need to use the CheezeScape one.
Any help appreciated. Thanks.
~Tiger
